input_str: FirefoxOS has been my main focus over quite a period of time now. I worked with the system, I helped developers port their apps to it and I spend hours and hours writing about it, making demos and talking to the press and anyone who’d stand still long enough (or sit on a plane next to me). Today I got my reward with the FirefoxOS movement going from “Idea” via “Prototype” to “Developer Preview” and now “Launch”
